plyTime":"2017-03-14T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"我係夢境都係做毒撚,點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007eebd80facc1cb245bc24f47769bdfd481c84d","tid":156062,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係夢境都係做毒撚,點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係相反既恭喜你喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73c600cb52a8fd2db062ada5f1aae4c04d8cdb3","tid":156062,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"發左個好sweet既夢又唔記得細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c7f0c0b0200dbb50601a28b67fefa502dfb4df","tid":156062,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8042c8bcd060db1e740b3b5fb87a57501daa198","tid":156062,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"有冇試過陪發夢屋企人出事 <br />\n嚇到個心離一離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}